[2]
Date: Tue, 08 Jul 1997 10:18:59 -0400
From: John Mackenzie <jmac@biosci.uq.edu.au>
In answer to the Moderator's question about whether specimens were collected
from the influenza outbreak reported from Finschafen area in PNG and sent for
typing, I understand no specimens were received by the WHO Collaborating
Centre for Influenza Reference and Research in Melbourne (Dr. Alan Hampson).
---
John Mackenzie
